World rankings points
The Tour de France was one of 29Â events throughout the season that contributed points towards the 2012 UCI World Tour. Points were awarded to the top 20Â finishers overall, and to the top five finishers in each stage. Only riders on UCI ProTour teams were eligible to receive rankings points.28



