Prize money
In total, around &lt;U+20AC&gt;3.5 million was distributed during the Tour. Initially, each team received &lt;U+20AC&gt;51,243, while each team with at least seven riders finishing the Tour received &lt;U+20AC&gt;1600 per rider. The winner of the General Classification received &lt;U+20AC&gt;450,000, with smaller prizes for each finishing position, down to &lt;U+20AC&gt;400 for the last rider.31

